For one night only Jamie Oliver brings the truth about junk food to a captive 
audience of fast food junkies. It will be a graphic and uncompromising 
revelation of the food we eat and what it does to us.
Eat To Save Your Life will follow the life cycle of junk food as it churns its 
way through the body, They will use extraordinary filming techniques and 
shocking stunts to take the audience through every detail about the crippling 
effect of the rubbish we eat, including the autopsy by renowned anatomist 
Dr Gunther von Hagens of a 159 kilogram man who literally ate himself to death.
